%spark
import se.uu.it.mare._
val recordDelimiter = "\n$$$$\n"
sc.hadoopConfiguration.set("textinputformat.record.delimiter", recordDelimiter)
val rdd = sc.textFile("hdfs://spark-marco-3-master-000/aksci")
new MaRe(rdd).map(
    inputMountPoint = TextFile("/input.sdf", recordDelimiter),
    outputMountPoint = TextFile("/output.sdf", recordDelimiter),
    imageName = "mcapuccini/oe:latest",
    command = "fred -receptor /var/openeye/hiv1_protease.oeb " +
        "-hitlist_size 0 " +
        "-conftest none " +
        "-dbase /input.sdf " +
        "-docked_molecule_file /output.sdf"
).reduce(
    inputMountPoint = TextFile("/input.sdf", recordDelimiter),
    outputMountPoint = TextFile("/output.sdf", recordDelimiter),
    imageName = "mcapuccini/sdsorter:latest",
    command = "sdsorter -reversesort='FRED Chemgauss4 score' " +
        "-keep-tag='FRED Chemgauss4 score' " +
        "-nbest=30 " +
        "/input.sdf " +
        "/output.sdf"
).rdd.map(_+"\n$$$$").saveAsTextFile("hdfs://spark-marco-3-master-000/aksci_top30")
// Took 1 hrs 6 min 25 sec.
